msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/date"
msgid "June 6th, 1944 · Brécourt Manor, Normandy, France."
msgstr "6 de junio de 1944. Mansión de Brécourt, Normandía, Francia."

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/ending"
msgid ""
"The successful assault at Brécourt Manor, in part, gave the troops at Utah "
"Beach a relatively easy landing. This assault has become a classic case "
"study in military training for engaging a superior enemy force. Colonel "
"Robert Sink, who commanded the 506th Parachute Infantry Regiment, put "
"forward Dick Winters for the Medal of Honor. Still, it was downgraded to the "
"Distinguished Service Cross due to a policy allowing only one Medal of Honor "
"per division. Despite this, both Winters and Lieutenant Speirs would later "
"gain global recognition for their actions at Brécourt Manor and in "
"subsequent battles."
msgstr ""
"El exitoso asalto en la mansión de Brécour ayudó a las tropas en la playa de "
"Utah a tener un desembarco relativamente fácil. Este asalto se ha convertido "
"en un caso clásico de entrenamiento militar para enfrentarse a una fuerza "
"enemiga superior. El coronel Robert Sink, que mandaba el 506º Regimiento de "
"Infantería Paracaidista, propuso a Dick Winters para recibir la Medalla de "
"Honor. Sin embargo, fue degradado a la Cruz de Servicio Distinguido debido a "
"una política que sólo permitía una Medalla de Honor por división. A pesar de "
"ello, tanto Winters como el teniente Speirs obtendrían más tarde el "
"reconocimiento mundial por sus acciones en Brécourt y en batallas "
"posteriores."

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/name"
msgid "Hold Fast!"
msgstr "¡Al asalto!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/name_big"
msgid "Hold Fast!"
msgstr "¡Al asalto!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator01"
msgid ""
"Easy Company, Listen Up! Our boys on Utah beach are getting hammered by that "
"Kraut artillery. Drop everything except weapons and ammo!"
msgstr ""
"Compañía Easy, ¡escuchad! Nuestros chicos en la playa Utah están siendo "
"machacados por esa artillería alemana ¡Soltad todo menos armas y munición!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator02"
msgid ""
"Our main objective is to destroy the enemy howitzer battery. Use TNT or "
"satchel charges!"
msgstr ""
"Nuestro objetivo principal es destruir la batería de obuses enemiga ¡Utiliza "
"TNT o cargas explosivas!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator03"
msgid ""
"After we're done with the howitzers, we'll need to clear the Germans from "
"the nearby manor."
msgstr ""
"Cuando acabemos con los obuses, tendremos que sacar a los alemanes de la "
"mansión cercana."

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator04"
msgid ""
"We'll use the .30 cal machine guns to set a base of fire and assault the "
"enemy artillery from the flank. We'll get in close, then hit them hard and "
"fast."
msgstr ""
"Utilizaremos las ametralladoras del calibre 30 para crear una cortina de "
"fuego y asaltaremos esa artillería enemiga por el flanco. Nos acercaremos y "
"luego les daremos fuerte y rápido."

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator05"
msgid "Avoid the open field to the east, or they'll spot us!"
msgstr "¡Evita el campo abierto al este, o nos descubrirán!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator06"
msgid "Great job! We destroyed the guns!"
msgstr "¡Gran trabajo! ¡Hemos destruido los cañones!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator07"
msgid "We need to take out that MG42 on the other side of the field!"
msgstr "¡Tenemos que eliminar esa MG42 del otro lado del campo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator08"
msgid "Excellent! That MG42 is not a threat anymore!"
msgstr "¡Excelente! ¡Esa MG42 ya no es una amenaza!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator09"
msgid "Now we need to take the manor! Let's go!"
msgstr "¡Ahora tenemos que tomar la mansión! ¡Adelante, muchachos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator10"
msgid "The manor is ours! Good job!"
msgstr "¡La mansión es nuestra! ¡Buen trabajo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator11"
msgid ""
"Stay out of the open field in front of the cannons! They'll stop firing at "
"the beaches and instead start fire at us!"
msgstr ""
"¡Cuidado con cruzar por el campo frente a los cañones! ¡Dejarán de disparar "
"a las playas y empezarán a dispararnos a nosotros!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator12"
msgid ""
"Enemy infantry, coming from the east! Get one of those .30 cals over here "
"and pour it on them!"
msgstr ""
"Infantería enemiga, ¡viene del este! ¡Trae uno de esos calibres 30 y "
"machácalos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator13"
msgid "Hey Lieutenant Speirs. We appreciate Dog Company's help today."
msgstr ""
"Hola Teniente Speirs Agradecemos la ayuda de la Compañía D (\"Dog\") hoy."

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator14"
msgid "Yeah, sure. Here you go."
msgstr "Sí, claro. Aquí tienes."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator_gun1"
msgid "One down, three to go!"
msgstr "Uno menos, ¡quedan tres!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator_gun2"
msgid "Another one destroyed! On to the next gun!"
msgstr "¡Otro destruida! ¡A por el siguiente cañón!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator_gun3"
msgid "There's only one left! Let's go!"
msgstr "¡Sólo queda uno! ¡Venga!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator_secret"
msgid ""
"I can't see a thing... Maybe I could see better if I climbed up this tree..."
msgstr "No veo nada... Quizá podría ver mejor si me subiera a este árbol..."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator_speirs1"
msgid "D Company here! We figured you could use some help!"
msgstr "¡Aquí la Compañía D! ¡Pensamos que te vendría bien un poco de ayuda!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator_speirs2"
msgid "Looks like they've had enough. "
msgstr "Parece que ya han tenido suficiente."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator_speirs3"
msgid "... Hey, you got some cigarettes?"
msgstr "...Oye ¿Tienes cigarrillos?"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator_speirs4"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator_tank"
msgid ""
"Hey! We could use some help over here! Blow up these obstacles so we can get "
"through!"
msgstr ""
"¡Eh! ¡Necesitamos ayuda por aquí! ¡Vuela estos obstáculos para que podamos "
"pasar!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/narrator_tank2"
msgid "Thanks! We were sitting ducks!"
msgstr "¡Gracias! ¡Éramos presa fácil!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"You failed to complete the primary objective! Because we did not silence the "
"enemy artillery, our boys on Utah Beach took heavy damage. You must try "
"again!"
msgstr ""
"¡No has conseguido completar el objetivo principal! Como no detuvimos a la "
"artillería enemiga, nuestros chicos de Utah sufrieron muchas bajas ¡Debes "
"intentarlo de nuevo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/outro_completed"
msgid ""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/place"
msgid "101st Airborne Division \"Screaming Eagles\""
msgstr "101ª División Aerotransportada \"Screaming Eagles\""

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/situation1"
msgid "Brécourt Manor - 08:35 hours"
msgstr "Mansión de Brécourt. 08:35 horas"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/situation2"
msgid "E (\"Easy\") Company, 2nd Battalion, 506th Parachute Infantry Regiment"
msgstr ""
"Compañía E (\"Easy\"), 2º Batallón, 506º Regimiento de Infantería "
"Aerotransportada"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/story"
msgid ""
"  6th of June, 1944. It’s been about 7 hours since you made the 'Big Jump'.\n"
"\n"
"  You have spent most of the night moving towards your main objective and "
"regrouping with your Easy Company comrades along the way. After daybreak, "
"you arrive at Le Grand Chemin, a small village between Ste Marie du Mont and "
"Utah Beach.\n"
"\n"
"  The main task of securing the Utah Beach causeways is far from complete. "
"The company’s Headquarters Section is missing in action this morning, so "
"your orders are to report to Battalion HQ, Lieutenant Winters.\n"
"\n"
" Good luck!"
msgstr ""
"  6 de junio de 1944. Han pasado unas 7 horas desde que diste el \"gran "
"salto\".\n"
"\n"
"  Has pasado la mayor parte de la noche avanzando hacia tu objetivo "
"principal y reagrupándote con tus camaradas de la Compañía Easy por el "
"camino. Al amanecer, llegas a Le Grand Chemin, un pequeño pueblo entre Ste "
"Marie du Mont y la playa Utah.\n"
"\n"
"  La tarea principal de asegurar los caminos y posiciones cerca de la playa "
"Utah está lejos de completarse. No eres capaz de encontrar la sección del "
"cuartel general de la compañía esta mañana, por lo que tus órdenes son "
"presentarte en el cuartel general del batallón, Teniente Winters.\n"
"\n"
" ¡Buena suerte!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/task1"
msgid "Sabotage the enemy howitzers!"
msgstr "¡Sabotea los obuses enemigos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/task2"
msgid "Neutralize the enemy machine gun!"
msgstr "¡Neutraliza la ametralladora enemiga!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/task3"
msgid "Capture the manor!"
msgstr "¡Captura la mansión!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/task4"
msgid "Destroy the roadblock."
msgstr "Destruye la barricada."

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/task_secret"
msgid "(Secret objective) Climb up the tree"
msgstr "(Objetivo secreto) Trepa el árbol"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/task_secret_noncomp"
msgid "(Secret objective)"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto nº 1"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/task_speirs"
msgid "Lt. Speirs must survive."
msgstr "El teniente Speirs debe sobrevivir."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_03_brecourt_manor/task_winters"
msgid "Lt. Winters must survive."
msgstr "El teniente Winters debe sobrevivir."
